a4c25fb26a98261adcf74506e3d6b5b27e6334f47b219239a37fba109e75d6f20be9d0febfbf1c6caabf4a9b813bdd1fd1ff557f1f4b53fe36333a939c7ecfcc  0001-ut_mimserveroptions-Move-the-operator-definition-to-.patch
